{"tid":2039453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請勿各大文宣PAGE，切勿再濫用「叫春式情緒勒索文宣」。","createTime":"2020-05-28T04:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T06:23:26.000Z","uid":34676,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"08593940fa2413ee2c536da90c58b9e3ff4ac68c","tid":2039453,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ed4H9Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ed4H9Y.jpg&h=faabeb55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DViTBuY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDViTBuY.jpg&h=b34a654b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOndBuZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOndBuZ.jpg&h=9fc114d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NPUvDJj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNPUvDJj.jpg&h=f99f0644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HRygzgF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHRygzgF.jpg&h=b81fd5ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipc89P0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fipc89P0.jpg&h=63dd176d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoAbn91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoAbn91.jpg&h=acf82c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2z0gu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2z0gu1.jpg&h=e2a783ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以往嘅文宣，係充滿資訊性，每個Page都少有地放負，教你應咩活動做咩事，有咩注意既事項。<br />\n<br />\n但唔知幾時開始，文宣界就充斥住好多低成本，黑底白字好似心情日記咁，充斥住各Page編輯嘅所有情緒，嬲又要出一個文宣，放負又要出一個文宣，想單單打打又要出一個文宣，甚至會出現好似內容農場咁用嘩眾取寵作為開首內容。令分享嘅人互相批鬥。<br />\n<br />\n我會突然想分享，係因為尋日實在睇得太多人Share 上自己story，再加埋一ｄ自己嘅意見，例如係：「岩啊，成班人叫極都唔郁，光咩復香港靠把口 bla bla bla  冇撚用架喇，下下都送頭，咩都唔好做囉。根本夠人就唔需要驚。」呢類形文宣厲害之處就係會令分享者陷入批鬥屌票既循環當中，有出去既就喺STORY就批鬥冇出去既，冇出去既就喺STORY批鬥出去既送頭，付出多就喺STORY批鬥付出少既，有罷工既就喺STORY批鬥冇罷工，冇罷工既就喺STORY批鬥活動事前無準備，大家口中就係：岩啊岩啊，呢個文宣講出我心聲。<br />\n<br />\n乜呢個係文宣既責任咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢D 負面散播就係你地想做既野?甚至我仲見到有D PAGE 好小學生咁扭計：「警告你地，如果聽唔出去既話，請你UNFOL 我吧。」「如果再唔全城勇武，呢場運動不如現在結束就算。」我想講，你地傻撚左啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n運動持續接近一年，大家都明白文宣嘅意義係用嚟推動成個運動，而唔係脅逼參與其中既人。以上例子嘅文宣編輯，講得難聽Ｄ，你地講野根本唔需要負上任何責任。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我請各IG 文宣手足，唔好再當自己個PAGE 係XANGA 、blog 咁有咩情緒就投放哂落去。唔好打着文宣嘅殼，去情緒勒索任何人。更加唔好再濫用最後一戰云云等字眼。因為一時三刻見唔到成效，因為手足做一兩件錯事就去放棄所有野，本來就係一件好戇鳩既事。"},{"pid":"85931848b52100ca637b5356fb62ba3dec6d66f5","tid":2039453,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"[文宣方向][跳出同溫層]民意調查分析<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037458</a>"},{"pid":"fb968b298db37df812dcc8594d3834dd7698ef73","tid":2039453,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"覺得我講得啱嘅就幫忙一推"},{"pid":"0b2659b5fdfe66aff4e2d828efe08a114624d154","tid":2039453,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efe6222815e4eace3518e69304b15092344b6d53","tid":2039453,"uid":57009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1696c593789268bdd1706a1b1dd49901719b296","tid":2039453,"uid":19889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"我知某d圖係來自邊d page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認同"},{"pid":"78777f7e5ee1f020cba6f2a3bdda0ce8c2ac85be","tid":2039453,"uid":184801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"